column16: Nationals challenged (force play), call on the field was upheld: Ryan Zimmerman grounds into a force out, third baseman Adonis Garcia to second baseman Jace Peterson.   Wilmer Difo out at 2nd.
Wilmer Difo singles on a line drive to left fielder Matt Kemp.
Danny Espinosa called out on strikes.
Ben Revere grounds out, second baseman Jace Peterson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Jayson Werth singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Matt Kemp.   Trea Turner scores.
Trea Turner hits a ground-rule double (13) on a line drive to left field.
Brian Goodwin grounds into a double play, second baseman Gordon Beckham to shortstop Dansby Swanson to first baseman Blake Lalli.   Stephen Drew out at 2nd.
Stephen Drew singles on a line drive to center fielder Ender Inciarte.
Christian Yelich grounds out to first baseman Freddie Freeman.   Martin Prado to 3rd.
Martin Prado reaches on a fielding error by second baseman Jace Peterson.
Ichiro Suzuki grounds out, second baseman Jace Peterson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Bartolo Colon bunt pops into a double play, catcher A.  J.   Pierzynski to second baseman Jace Peterson.   Travis d'Arnaud doubled off 1st.
Travis d'Arnaud singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Ender Inciarte, deflected by second baseman Jace Peterson.
Kelly Johnson grounds out, first baseman Freddie Freeman to pitcher Shae Simmons.
Jayson Werth pops out to shortstop Dansby Swanson.
Trea Turner doubles (11) on a line drive to right fielder Nick Markakis.  Trea Turner advances to 3rd, on a fielding error by right fielder Nick Markakis.
Brian Goodwin grounds out, third baseman Adonis Garcia to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Danny Espinosa strikes out swinging, catcher Tyler Flowers to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Aaron Altherr grounds out, shortstop Dansby Swanson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Cesar Hernandez grounds out, pitcher Shae Simmons to second baseman Jace Peterson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Jimmy Paredes grounds out softly, second baseman Jace Peterson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Travis Jankowski grounds out, second baseman Jace Peterson to first baseman Freddie Freeman.
Adam Rosales pops out to second baseman Jace Peterson.
Brett Wallace lines out to left fielder Matt Kemp.
